Created a train ticket booking system using Datas trutures and algorithms.which allows to book train ticket and login to portal using c++.
Implemented hashmaps for creating user profile using keys as usernames and values as passwords.
created different class one for trains ans one for the users and implemented train methods and customer methods respectively.
used a switch case for selecting the task they wanted to perform.indicating with the respective feedback.like selecting the boarding point,departure and destination and intimated the users with feedback.
created a structure for trains that describes if the tickets avalable or not for each train.
